26#ifndef NetworkCacheIOChannel_h
27#define NetworkCacheIOChannel_h
28
29#include "NetworkCacheData.h"
30#include <wtf/Function.h>
31#include <wtf/ThreadSafeRefCounted.h>
32#include <wtf/WorkQueue.h>
33#include <wtf/text/WTFString.h>
34
35#if USE(GLIB)
36#include <wtf/glib/GRefPtr.h>
37
38typedef struct _GFileIOStream GFileIOStream;
39typedef struct _GInputStream GInputStream;
40typedef struct _GOutputStream GOutputStream;
41#endif
42
43namespace WebKit {
44namespace NetworkCache {
45
46class IOChannel : public ThreadSafeRefCounted<IOChannel> {
47public:
48 enum class Type { Read, Write, Create };
49 static Ref<IOChannel> open(const String& file, Type type, std::optional<WorkQueue::QOS> qos = { }) { return adoptRef(*new IOChannel(file, type, qos)); }
50
51 // Using nullptr as queue submits the result to the main queue.
52 // FIXME: We should add WorkQueue::main() instead.
53 void read(size_t offset, size_t, WorkQueue&, Function<void (Data&, int error)>&&);
54 void write(size_t offset, const Data&, WorkQueue&, Function<void (int error)>&&);
55
56 const String& path() const { return m_path; }
57 Type type() const { return m_type; }
58
59#if !USE(GLIB)
60 bool isOpened() const { return FileSystem::isHandleValid(m_fileDescriptor); }
61#else
62 bool isOpened() const { return true; }
63#endif
64
65 ~IOChannel();
66
67private:
68 IOChannel(const String& filePath, IOChannel::Type, std::optional<WorkQueue::QOS>);
69
70#if USE(GLIB)
71 void readSyncInThread(size_t offset, size_t, WorkQueue&, Function<void (Data&, int error)>&&);
72#endif
73
74 String m_path;
75 Type m_type;
76
77#if !USE(GLIB)
78 FileSystem::PlatformFileHandle m_fileDescriptor { FileSystem::invalidPlatformFileHandle };
79#endif
80 std::atomic<bool> m_wasDeleted { false }; // Try to narrow down a crash, https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=165659
81#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
82 OSObjectPtr<dispatch_io_t> m_dispatchIO;
83#endif
84#if USE(GLIB)
85 GRefPtr<GInputStream> m_inputStream;
86 GRefPtr<GOutputStream> m_outputStream;
87 GRefPtr<GFileIOStream> m_ioStream;
88#endif
89};
90
91}
92}
93
94#endif
